<h2>Tooltip trigger</h2>

<p>By default the tooltip will attach itself to the parent DOM element, but there are ways to customize this:</p>

<div class="bs-example">
    <!-- BEGIN-SNIPPET tooltip-target -->
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default">DOM parent
        {{bs-tooltip title="DOM parent"}}
    </button>

    {{#bs-button}}Parent component
        {{bs-tooltip triggerElement="parentView" title="Parent component"}}
    {{/bs-button}}

    <button id="Tooltip-button" class="btn btn-default">jQuery selector</button>
    {{bs-tooltip triggerElement="#Tooltip-button" title="jQuery selector"}}

    <!-- END-SNIPPET -->
</div>
